com.valensas.vlsync.lib

Class VLSync

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.valensas.vlsync.lib.VLSync

  • public class VLSync
extends java.lang.Object
    VLSync is used to handle file synchronization between your mobile application and your VLSync project on web.

    Created on 1/19/15
    Created @ Valensas
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:

    See Also:

      • update

        public void update(java.util.Map<VLSync.UpdateOptionKey,VLSync.UpdateOptionValue> options)
        Starts update process with options. If VLSync.HUDState is set to VLSync.HUDState.VISIBLE, a Context reference must be passed to update function in order to show progress HUD.
        Parameters:
        options - desired options. If the same option given twice, last one is set.
        Since:
        1.0
        See Also:
        update(), VLSync.UpdateOptionKey, VLSync.HUDState

      • update

          android.content.Context context)
        Starts update process with options. If VLSync.HUDState is set to VLSync.HUDState.VISIBLE, a Context reference must be passed to update function in order to show progress HUD.
        Parameters:
        options - desired options. If the same option given twice, last one is set.
        context - necessary to display HUD
        Since:
        1.0
        See Also:
        update(android.content.Context), VLSync.UpdateOptionKey, VLSync.HUDState
